Monday Morning Rewind: Bud Grant does not own a jacket Bud, seriously, why? Feb 6, 2017 at 10:59a ET 0 
Keeping track of all the best videos on the internet can be a full-time job. 
Fortunately for you, it’s our full-time job. 
To start off your week, we bring you some of the videos you might have missed the past seven days. 
So sit back, relax and enjoy. 
It’s now officially a fact: Bud Grant does not own a jacket. Call your buds and join me at @Vikings #WinterFest in Prior Lake February 16-18! #Vikings https://t.co/m2miy1lKAC pic.twitter.com/DVskQ26fXo
